Join Our Webinar: Industry Update - the latest market developments in Air Freight & Ocean Freight

Thursday 5 December 2024, 10:00AM - 11:00 AM AEST
  
Please join us for our final 2024 webinar covering news and developments in the international air freight and ocean freight market. Our product leaders will cover relevant topics on key global tradelanes, carriers and local infrastructure.

Our presenters John Santomartino - Head of Air Freight and Taylor Williams Head of Ocean Freight are also available to answer your questions. 

We look forward to your participation.
